0:00:00.260,0:00:04.840
Minyengetero yose yawanga uchisimbirira - iwe wanga uchinyengetera, uchitsanya -

0:00:04.840,0:00:13.260
kubva nhasi, unogona kuita zvinhu zvose kuburikidza na Jesu Kristu uyo anokusimbisa.

0:00:13.260,0:00:21.340
Iti, ndinogona kuita zvinhu zvose kubudikidza na Kristu Jesu anondisimbisa,

0:00:21.340,0:00:29.120
muzita ra Jesu!

0:00:29.120,0:00:36.580
Kwete kuti iwe wakakonzera asi nekuti Jesu anozodza avo vaanosarudza kuzodza.

0:00:36.580,0:00:45.940
Asarudza iwe nhasi! Iwe uri akasarudzwa!

0:00:45.940,0:00:51.340
Udza waugere naye: Handikodzere; Akasarudza kusarudza ini.

0:00:51.340,0:00:56.680
Anosarudza waanosarudza; Anoda waanoda.

0:00:56.680,0:01:04.760
Ndazodzwa nhasi, muzita ra Jesu!

0:01:10.300,0:01:16.720
Tambanudza ruoko rwako mberi!

0:01:16.720,0:01:18.960
Tanga kuisa ruoko rwako izvozvi -

0:01:18.960,0:01:22.940
ruoko rwakazodzwa, ruoko rworudyi rwa Mwari!

0:01:22.940,0:01:29.360
Avo vanesu, avo vari kwatiri, vari kunyengetera nesu!

0:01:29.360,0:01:36.380
Tambanudza ruoko rwako! Iwe uchanzwa kudedera, huvepo hwa Mwari

0:01:36.380,0:01:45.380
sezvazvinofanira kuve, nekuda kwa Mwari, muzita ra Jesu!

0:01:45.380,0:01:50.700
Iti, sezvazvinofanira kuve, nekuda kwa Mwari!

0:01:50.700,0:01:56.100
Chimwe chinhu chitsvene hachikwanisi kuva chese chese.

0:01:56.100,0:01:59.800
Kana chiri chemazuva ose, iwe hauna kukodzera.

0:01:59.800,0:02:04.660
Udza waugere naye: Chimwe chinhu chitsvene hachigoni kuve chemazuva ose.

0:02:04.660,0:02:11.060
Dai zvaive zve mazuva ese, dai yaiva hama yako, dai aiva T.B. Joshua

0:02:11.060,0:02:14.280
anga achipa izvozvo, pamwe haaigona kundipa.

0:02:14.280,0:02:20.720
Asi Mwari anosarudza sezva Anoda.

0:02:25.560,0:02:29.480
Muzita rakasimba ra Jesu!

0:02:29.480,0:02:34.360
Ruoko rumwe norumwe rwatambanudzwa, ngaruzodzwe!

0:02:34.360,0:02:38.860
Rurimi rwose rwataura, ngaruzodzwe!

0:02:38.860,0:02:51.220
Ruoko rworudyi rwa Mwari isimba!

0:02:51.220,0:02:59.540
Iti, ruoko rworudyi rwa Mwari isimba!

0:02:59.540,0:03:03.200
Iti, rurimi!

0:03:03.200,0:03:23.060
Ndagamuchira rurimi kuti ndisunungure ne kusunga, muzita ra Jesu!

0:03:23.060,0:03:27.080
Apo munyengetero we ruzhinji waitungamirirwa nemu Porofita T.B. Joshua,

0:03:27.080,0:03:30.100
zviuru zvevanhu zvakagamuchira kuporeswa pakarepo.

0:03:30.100,0:03:36.080
Mumwe mukadzi - chishamiso Mweya Mutsvene wakabvisa bundu repa chibereko,

0:03:36.080,0:03:39.080
achinyengetera pamwechete nomu Porofita T.B. Joshua.

0:03:39.080,0:03:43.640
Kana simba ra Mwari riripo, kuporeswa kwakafanana nekufema,

0:03:43.640,0:03:51.340
dzikinuro inofanana nokufema uye kubudirira kunofanana nekufema.

0:03:51.340,0:03:54.540
Nguva yezvishamiso haina kupfuura.

0:03:54.540,0:03:57.140
Muiti wezvishamiso achiri mupenyu.

0:03:57.140,0:03:59.680
Zita rake ndi Jesu Kristu.

0:03:59.680,0:04:02.300
Vatariri pasi pose, ngatitarirei.

0:04:02.300,0:04:04.760
Tarisa pasikirini ye terevhizheni yako.

0:04:04.760,0:04:08.960
Uyu ndiye mukadzi uyo auya nhasi ane dambudziko re mapundu akawanda muchibereko

0:04:08.960,0:04:13.980
Apo munyengetero wanga uchienderera mberi nemunhu wa Mwari, mapundu acho atanga kubuda kubva mumuviri wake.

0:04:13.980,0:04:18.760
Mapundu Emuchibereko Anoputika

0:04:18.760,0:04:22.600
Chero chipi zvacho chisingabvi kuna Mwari, pauchabva pano uchienda kuchimbudzi,

0:04:22.600,0:04:26.760
iwe uchatanga kubuditsa izvo zvisiri chikamu chehupenyu hwako.

0:04:26.760,0:04:30.060
Nderipi dambudziko mubhizinesi rako?

0:04:30.060,0:04:33.980
Uchashandisa muromo wako kusunungura ne kusunga.

0:04:33.980,0:04:37.360
Mari yako ichadzorerwa.

0:04:37.360,0:04:41.620
Muchato wako uchagadziriswa.

0:04:41.620,0:04:43.220
Ndinokutendai, Ishe.

0:04:43.220,0:04:44.840
Ndiri kufara nekuda kwehupenyu hwako.

0:04:44.840,0:04:50.720
Tinovimba kuti wakurudzirwa nevhidhiyo yawabva mukuona.

0:04:50.720,0:04:57.260
Tinya apa kuti unyorese kupupurira zvakawanda pamusoro pesimba ra Mwari pabasa munguva yatiri nhasi

0:04:57.260,0:05:01.480
kuti ugare uri pamusoro pezvichagoburwa zvehuporofita,dzikinuro,

0:05:01.480,0:05:06.400
mharidzo nezvapupu zvinobva ku Synagogue Church Of All Nations

